cus on the active parts. It might be best to avoid unrelated topics. I may need to update the reflect-config to ensure it’s sorted correctly. It started with NativeJavaObject, then moved to Global, so that might work. I should also read the full file to check the trailing comma syntax.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0ede3b943cc81bd70169f4fd063b3c819e8dfa4e8bb5721b7a\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp9P0RGj1ImUqQpQvHutWl3CIHo3XX7i1UPOCa4_CDxLjvdB-nLLwW66ufbhiZQBXUFobRVILgpQf7WyzqjuFzHt9OpAtIBrF3Tf85a6-GfCTEzboBjT9yJvw2ZWDzOTCCBlg3mVnJqbXOqbvAD8Kw3olyyiRfoGE-kh_On_-edzpmRgMwSfXwgT62SmMvNrN2q1VieUEQ0nCPmdDD2mGao2J5yarC4xCGBt81GdwBHkliLjJo-I0PLpdTKbRiQ8y0mrlCVB3TRsi5HFHeMH3u_g3mgt5qpWYePoCK7i8l3ku_Jlgm1rW_hHXA0sYTyZ2rckvO-2A_jbgU4uLhhWnXXIljVORWScfnautiNFKglsUGYp3BVND1P2Ya5vQ_IGIKkIixmZGgX1hOfrzVMvkrwmKQRnZJV1Nf6xxLJT7UivLaJGgjOfluufkLwV1OZfrtzIG7O7Nzxb8VqZwopShKEcsj7aA3Q0Cj0nglUJ2ndEuhbJbPx4JzfbUHXNBOxhtTOGCuB-0pfL7nUf3j_lARJSAVzTytdXsGXwYpI88Ke6jb5tze46u03x9Gfrn3JdqQ6-ldCc6_xcheixhmL08CUkb4oTZCZawZyglpuZQHcJiW42E5D-yl3LrBK1GXMlmRTBoNLJiBwyIz01FTiKaO9RTMWmPyapeR_gxNE9NETt4dW4Oox5M9t6RzzXNEwq9T_hdM56HGB0mqxnlsB065meB73lp_GNGlpUdFSwAn73etOj5E50D70QHvjLGbTTdXFSy1VZ69PTQluvVSeJkWwcVX-kp09UJOBfYd00D9utEciT2Qg5NoGC24uwX0l4D8cDYjO44w7TDaPQ-R3LBurUipyqlbJLk7wNJVp9eauPkFe5sHX4XpkWbKXF5wOKhClwzMG3uJdOs1AXAlKOtV6mj4FzhbHrlNPER7zovsnwKf-jh59vlx1iMiDFVOyzg37tjabj5n8bxH93pUhKNiSMmpVwsXHoNO_T2Pibvz6htTPzXHCsYnvCT25tK-7kqFpE_Pr8EKrN-KCtuKrdt3450HbmOc4Z2rKuTmHv0ujm6wh1f6cwAC1D2CY6mBlQtKpoLKiM3R1JeVfuRY5L86ejjNSB3gDqyF67yrd6DaI4_qZ8CdHwSzzzmBxz9ku8LMS13KeaA1scynz4iug486L_cRdvKy7YfhqI6_iEikEn2NxWH38nYERLCFCxZHpm9rNE5B0VnZmlzLOqKsTQe6lvLgPUXA1OGC0ERkOpBfgzCnUeLHYHYMOI0sbZcTez7hAdhFgXKDjxvI6sB6FUk7XJhwGa31IjNhJJcReI7ECQcT2OuT5h38O0FC05VAsX4Lfd4OhAvRt1ARHD52gA6KjF5E3EJcfO4RYLFw-Swm5QSvoObpPv_bH85Ug_UyZIVgpR_3Wm1qSGj31VNPS1QWJ1lkRwrj3ywNgceT-qRb2FQw8x72y6PbKUt5eVS30OXeh-z6MpKV607j8tZGKFF55XbTbUoPabq-J7LQzLCeVS5dD48JSMH0Ki5bKXAPQXXM5v3ZH_9YwYHDGdg95gPJdwY8aHGrQOrE